<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <style>
    body { 
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6; 
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
    }
    .container { 
      max-width: 600px; 
      margin: 40px auto; 
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .header { 
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7c3aed 0%, #a78bfa 100%);
      color: white; 
      padding: 40px 30px; 
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .content { 
      padding: 40px 30px;
      background: #ffffff;
    }
    .content p {
      margin: 0 0 20px 0;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .cta-container {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    .button { 
      display: inline-block; 
      padding: 14px 32px; 
      background: #7c3aed;
      color: white !important;
      text-decoration: none; 
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 16px;
      transition: background 0.3s ease;
    }
    .button:hover {
      background: #6d28d9;
    }
    .support {
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #666;
    }
    .footer { 
      text-align: center; 
      padding: 20px 30px; 
      background: #f9fafb;
      color: #6b7280; 
      font-size: 13px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    }
    .footer p {
      margin: 5px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Welcome to FormaChat</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hey {{firstName}},</p>
      
      <p>Your FormaChat account is all set! You can now build AI-powered support agents that handle customer inquiries, bookings, and questions for your business â€” 24/7.</p>
      
      <p>Ready to create your first bot? Just log in and hit "Create Bot" to get started.</p>
      
      <div class="cta-container">
        <a href="https://formachat.com/dashboard" class="button">Go to Dashboard</a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="support">
        <p>Need help? Reach out anytime at <a href="mailto:support@formachat.com" style="color: #7c3aed; text-decoration: none;">support@formachat.com</a></p>
      </div>
      
      <p style="margin-top: 30px;">The FormaChat Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} FormaChat. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>If you didn't create this account, please ignore this email.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>